title: North Korea’s Hacker Army Behind 30% of Crypto Hacks This Year: Chainalysis
description: A Chainalysis report reveals North Korean hacking groups stole over $340 million in crypto this year, accounting for 30% of all crypto hacks.

title: Crypto Whale Cashes out Little-Known Altcoin After It Surged Over 200%
description: A wealthy cryptocurrency whale has recently transferred a nine-figure sum of a little-known Ethereum-based digital asset out of cryptocurrency exchanges after the value of the asset rose by more than 200%.
